"* [IO]Folder.open: with a nonexistent path panics the VM (unwrap on read_dir)
"* instead of throwing a catchable error.
{ var f = [IO]Folder.open:'/no/such/dir/quoin-audit-xyz'; f.path.print }.catch:{ |e|
    ('caught (correct): ' + e.s).print
}
'after folder open (only printed if the error was catchable)'.print
